<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const countOccurrences = (arr, value) => arr.reduce((a, v) => (v === value ? a + 1 : a + 0), 0);]]></content>
	<description>Counts the occurrences of a value in an array.  Use `Array.reduce()` to increment a counter each time you encounter the specific value inside the array.</description>
